</emphasis>
(female, holotype) reared from 
<taxonomicName box="[834,1073,1690,1714]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lauraceae" genus="Damburneya" kingdom="Plantae" order="Laurales" pageId="4" pageNumber="71" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="salicifolia">
